      <p>I know this is a bit late, but I wanted to give you an update. </></>I tried the recipe with asparagus, and either I didn&#8217;t cook it properly or I just really prefer the brussel sprouts. </></>I think the asparagus is a no go. Even cooking it for less time left it soggy and the sauce didn&#8217;t have that nuttiness from the brussel sprouts. </></>I will say your original recipe turned out beautifully, and has become a staple!</p>
