      <p>Molly &#8211; <br />I just made these and they were the sleeper hit of Christmas dinner.  My mother &#8211; an avowed HATER of brussels sprouts her whole life &#8211; ate them right up and declared her lifelong hatred of the sprouts OVER.  We made them with a bit of bacon, too.  It&#39;s Christmas&#8230;go all out, right?  Amazing.  You&#39;re right.  These are the new standard.</p>
    </div>

