    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Wow, long comment thread, going back years! I&#39;m a brussels sprout lover from Australia &#8211; sprout season is still going here.<br />Must check out All About Braising, because that is pretty much my cooking philosophy. In summer I do a lot of stirfries, but as someone somewhere pointed out, a classic Chinese stirfry is actually a braise, not a fried food.</p>
